// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4525 — Mass File Rename (ransomhub)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7ba2cc74-fa95-550c-af9c-98fa96110487

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
